SELECT 
      [Customer Name]
	   ,[Customer Header Reference]
      ,[Address Reference]
      ,[Site Use Code]
      ,[Primary Site Use Flag]
      ,[ Location]
      ,[Bill To Orig Address Reference]
      ,'' as [Address Line 1]
      ,'' as[Address Line 2]
      ,'' as [Address Line 3]
      ,'' as [Address Line 4]
      ,'' as [Address Lines Phonetic]
      ,[City]
      ,[Province]
      ,[State]
      ,[County]
      ,[Postal Code]
      ,[Country]
      ,'100020.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000.901745' as [Receivables Account]
      ,'XXXXXX.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Revenue Account]
      ,'100020.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Tax Account]
      ,'100020.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Freight Account]
      ,'100020.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Clearing Account]
      ,'100020.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Unbilled Receivables Account]
      ,'XXXXXX.11111100.0000.00.00.000000.000000.000000.000000. 901745' as [Unearned Revenue Account]
      ,[Payment Method Name]
      ,[Payment Method Primary Flag]
      ,[Customer Profile]
      ,[Site Use Tax Reference]
      ,[Time Zone]
      ,[Language]
      ,[Contributor Class at Account Site]
      ,[Use Cust Site Profile Flag at Account Site]
      ,[Contributor Class at Account Site Use]
      ,[Use Cust Site Profile Flag at Account Site Use]
      ,[Economic Activity]
      ,[Payment Term Name]
      ,[Concept Code (CR)]
      ,[Giro (CL)]
      ,[US Remit-to Address Mapping]
      ,[US Tax Area Id]
      ,[Union Local]
      ,[TAID User Override]
      ,[TAID Last Checked]
      ,[TAID Assignment Result]
      ,[TAID Confidence Indicator]
      ,[TAID Precision]
      ,[CRM Account]
	   ,[Operating Unit Name]
     
  FROM [dbo].[address]

source.sqlReaderQuery:
/****** Script for SelectTopNRows command from SSMS  ******/
SELECT  
      [Customer_Header_Reference] as [Customer Header Reference]
      ,[Address_Reference]
      --,[Phone_Country_Code]
      --,[Phone_Extension]
      ,[Contact_Reference]
      ,[Contact_Point Reference]
      ,[Contact_First_Name]
      ,[Contact_Last_Name]
      ,[Contact Point_Type]
      ,[Area_Code]
      ,[Telephone_Number]
	  ,CASE COALESCE([Phone_Extension],'')  when ''  then '' else [Phone_Extension] end as [Phone_Extension]
      ,[EMAIL_Address]
      ,[Invoice_Delivery_Method]
       ,[Operating_Unit_Name]
  FROM [customer].[CustomerBillToContacts]

/****** Script for SelectTopNRows command from SSMS  ******/
SELECT  
      [Customer_Header_Reference] as [Customer Header Reference]
      ,[Address_Reference]
      ,[Contact_Point_Type]
      ,[Contact_Point_Status]
      ,[Primary_Flag]
      ,[Contact_Point_Purpose]
      ,[Phone_Country_Code]
      ,[Phone_Area_Code]
      ,[Phone_Number]
        ,CASE COALESCE([Phone_Extension],'')  when ''  then '' else [Phone_Extension] end as [Phone_Extension]
      ,[Phone_Line_Type]
      ,[Email_Address]
      ,[Email_Format]
	 , [Operating_Unit_Name]
  FROM [customer].[CustomerContactPoints]

/****** Script for SelectTopNRows command from SSMS  ******/
SELECT  [Customer_Name]
      ,[Customer_Party_Reference_Number]
      ,[Customer_Account_Reference_Number]
      ,[Customer_Type]
      ,[Customer_Profile]
      ,'' as [Payment_Method_Name]
      ,'' as [Payment_Method_Primary_Flag]
      ,[Global_Customer_Flag]
      ,'' as [Origin_(AR)]
      ,'' as [Primary_ID_Type]
      ,'' as [Primary_ID_Validation_Digit]
      ,'' as [Taxpayer_ID]
      ,'' as [Fiscal_Classification_Type_Code]
      ,'' as [Fiscal_Classification_Code]
      ,'' as [Effective_Date_From]
      ,'' as [Document_Type_(CO)]
      ,'' as [Taxpayer_ID_(CO)]
      , '' as [Nature_(CO)]
      ,'' as [Regimen_(CO)]
      ,'' as [Special_Customer_Flag]
      ,[Operating_Unit_Name]
      ,'' as [Customer_Class_Code]
      ,[Payment_Term_Name]
      ,'' as [Order_Number_of_the_Cedula_(GT)]
      ,'' as [Register_Number_of_the_Cedula_(GT)]
      ,'' as [Document_Type_(SV)]
      ,'' as [Contributor_Registry_Number_(SV)]
      ,'' as [Person_Category_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Person_Type_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Document_Type_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Document_Number_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Last_Name_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Second_Last_Name_(PE)]
      ,'' as [First_Name_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Middle_Name_(PE)]
      ,'' as [Origin]
      ,'' as [Nature]
      ,'' as [Document_Type_(UY)]
      ,'' as [Perception_Agent_(PE)]
  FROM [customer].[header]

SELECT  [ITEM_NUMBER]

      ,[MAX_MINMAX_QUANTITY]

      ,[FIXED_ORDER_QUANTITY]

Sort1, JoinidentificationBuilding join(unit_id == Bank@{UnitId FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join1
unit1 sort(asc(unit_id, true)) ~> Sort1
Join7 derive(unit_id = unit_id,
		TechnicianNotes = TechnicianNotes,
		Identification = @(BANK=@(ElevatorBank_ViewID=ElevatorBank_ViewID,
		ElevatorBank_BankName=ElevatorBank_BankName,
		ElevatorBank_AccessCode=ElevatorBank_AccessCode),
		Building=@(Building_ViewID=Building_ViewID)),
		EQUIPMENT = @(Floors=Floors,
		NumberofFrontOpenings=NumberofFrontOpenings,
		NumberofRearOpenings=NumberofRearOpenings,
		Unit_CapacityLbs=Unit_CapacityLbs,
		UNITTYPE=UNITTYPE,
		Manufacturer=Manufacturer,
		Controller=Controller,
		Speed=Speed,
		DriveType=DriveType)) ~> DerivedColumn1
Bank derive(Bank = @(ElevatorBank_ViewID=ElevatorBank_ViewID,
		ElevatorBank_ExternalID=ElevatorBank_ExternalID,
		ElevatorBank_BankName=ElevatorBank_BankName,
		ElevatorBank_AccessCode=ElevatorBank_AccessCode),
		{Identification FK} = {Identification FK}) ~> BankArray
Identification1, BankArray join(Identification1@ID == {Identification FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinBankidentification
JoinBankidentification, BUILDING join(BankArray@{Identification FK} == BUILDING@{identification FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinidentificationBuilding
EQUIPMENT derive(EQUIPMENT = @(Floors=Floors,
		NumberofFrontOpenings=NumberofFrontOpenings,
		NumberofRearOpenings=NumberofRearOpenings),
		UnitId = {UnitId FK},
		ID = ID) ~> EQUIPMENTDC1
EQUIPMENTType, EQUIPMENTDC1 join({Equipment Id FK} == EQUIPMENTDC1@ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join2
Join2 derive(UNITTYPE = @(EquipmentType_ViewID=EquipmentType_ViewID,
		EquipmentType_ExternalID=EquipmentType_ExternalID,
		EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName=EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification,
		NumberofRearOpenings=EQUIPMENTType@NumberofRearOpenings,
		Unit_CapacityLbs=EQUIPMENTType@Unit_CapacityLbs,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName),
		{Equipment Id FK} = {Equipment Id FK}) ~> arrayType
Manufacturer, EQUIPMENT join({Equipment Id FK} == EQUIPMENT@ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join3
Join3 derive(Manufacturerarray = @(Manufacturer_VIEWId=Manufacturer_VIEWId,
		Manufacturer_ExternalID=Manufacturer_ExternalID,
		Manufacturer_Name1=Manufacturer_Name1,
		Manufacturer_Name2=Manufacturer_Name2,
		AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID=AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID)) ~> ManufacturerArray
Controller, EQUIPMENT join({Equipment Id FK} == ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join4
Join4 derive(controllerArray = @(Controller_Name1=Controller_Name1),
		{Equipment Id FK} = {Equipment Id FK}) ~> controllerArray
speed, EQUIPMENT join({Equipment Id FK} == EQUIPMENT@ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join5
Join5 derive(Speed = @(Speed_ViewID=Speed_ViewID,
		Speed_FPM=Speed_FPM),
		{Equipment Id FK} = {Equipment Id FK}) ~> speedArray
DriveType, EQUIPMENT join({Equipment Id FK} == EQUIPMENT@ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join6
Join6 derive(DriveTypeArray = @(DriveType_ViewID=DriveType_ViewID,
		DriveType_ExternalID=DriveType_ExternalID,
		DriveType_Name1=DriveType_Name1,
		DriveType_Name2=DriveType_Name2)) ~> DriveTypearray
Join1, EQUIPMENTDC join(unit_id == EQUIPMENTDC@{UnitId FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join7
arrayType, Manufacturer join(arrayType@{Equipment Id FK} == Manufacturer@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> joinmanufacter
joinmanufacter, Controller join(Manufacturer@{Equipment Id FK} == Controller@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinController
JoinController, speed join(arrayType@{Equipment Id FK} == speed@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Joinspeed
JoinDriveType derive(ArrayType = @(EquipmentType_ViewID=EquipmentType_ViewID,
		EquipmentType_ExternalID=EquipmentType_ExternalID,
		EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName=EquipmentType_Okeefe_EquipName,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipClassification,
		NumberofRearOpenings=EQUIPMENT@NumberofRearOpenings,
		Unit_CapacityLbs=EQUIPMENT@Unit_CapacityLbs,
		EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName=EquipmentType_TKE_EquipName),
		Manufacturer = @(Manufacturer_VIEWId=Manufacturer_VIEWId,
		Manufacturer_ExternalID=Manufacturer_ExternalID,
		Manufacturer_Name1=Manufacturer_Name1,
		Manufacturer_Name2=Manufacturer_Name2,
		AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID=AfterHoursCallbackRun_ExternalID),
		Controller = @(Controller_Name1=Controller_Name1),
		Speed = @(Speed_ViewID=Speed_ViewID,
		Speed_FPM=Speed_FPM),
		DriveType = @(DriveType_ViewID=DriveType_ViewID,
		DriveType_ExternalID=DriveType_ExternalID,
		DriveType_Name2=DriveType_Name2,
		DriveType_Name1=DriveType_Name1),

		Unit_CapacityLbs = EQUIPMENT@Unit_CapacityLbs,
		{UnitId FK} = EQUIPMENT@{UnitId FK}) ~> EQUIPMENTDC
Joinspeed, DriveType join(arrayType@{Equipment Id FK} == DriveType@{Equipment Id FK},
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDriveType
